snippet.title: Reaction to First Image of Amber Heard as Mera in Justice League!!!
snippet.description:
Hey, guys, welcome to another reaction video here on the EdWord where in tonight's video I'll be discussing my thoughts and initial reaction to  the first look at Amber Heard as Mera in Justice League. She looks good!!! As does the movie, from the behind-the-scenes featurette. I hope you are all just as excited and pumped as I am for this movie after seeing this image of Mera. Thanks for watching, don't forget to subscribe for more videos. 

Justice League is set to be released Nov 17, 2017

Check out my FB page: https://m.facebook.com/theedword2016/
